
SCIM mim file for for TeX-style input - derived from the latin-ltx.el Quail
package by TAKAHASHI Naoto <ntakahas@m17n.org> and Dave Love <fx@gnu.org>.

Install by copying tex.mim to /usr/share/m17n/

Choose an input method framework that will supports the M17N Input Method
Engine (for instance SCIM)

im-switch -l
im-switch -s scim

See: http://www.jw-stumpel.nl/stestu.html#T6.5.2 for more info

Log out and then back in and enjoy your new input method!



Note:

Debian package required to compile imelist executable:

libm17n-dev
